msgid ""
"There are lot of tricks you can accomplish, and lots of ways to abuse the"
" forking of the master."
msgstr ""

#: ../../MasterFIFO.rst:84
msgid ""
"Just take into account that corner-case problems can occur all over the "
"place, especially if you use the most complex features of uWSGI."
msgstr ""

